com.c77.androidstreamingclient.lib.rtp

Class RtpMediaDecoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.c77.androidstreamingclient.lib.rtp.RtpMediaDecoder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Decoder

    public class RtpMediaDecoder
extends java.lang.Object
implements Decoder
    Implementation of the decoder that uses RTP as transport protocol to decode H264 encoded frames. This object wraps up an Android API decoder and uses it to decode video frames.
    Author:
    Ayelen Chavez
